<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Prof. Zhe-Min Zheng passed away on 16 September 2021. He was a well-known orthopterist in China, and he made outstanding contributions to the taxonomy of Chinese grasshoppers. To honor him, we named this new species after him.</paragraph>
